<div class="row row-light">
    <div class="col-md-5 col-xs-offset-1 col-xs-10">
        <p class="message">ImgBot is a GitHub app designed to keep your image files optimized</p>
        <p class="text-center hidden-xs">
            <a class="btn btn-default" href="https://github.com/apps/ImgBot">Try it now</a>
